.TH csd-locate-pointer 1 "Oct 2014" "" "CAFE-SETTINGS-DAEMON"
.SH NAME
csd-locate-pointer \- create ripples around mouse pointer
.SH SYNOPSIS
csd-locate-pointer
.SH DESCRIPTION
The \fIcsd-locate-pointer\fR utility is a program that creates ripples (like throwing a stone into water)
around the mouse pointer. This helps to locate the position of the mousepointer.
.PP
With \fIcafe-settings-daemon\fR i is possible to assign a hotkey for evoking
the \fIcsd-locate-pointer\fR command.
